Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.68,0:00:35.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Piano!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.17,0:00:36.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Piano....
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.91,0:00:38.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I must play the piano!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.96,0:00:42.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mukyaaaaa!!!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.70,0:01:22.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Although it's a very strange Rachmaninoff,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.22,0:01:24.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,it's very interesting!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.79,0:01:27.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,However,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.11,0:01:30.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,it cannot be harmonized in an orchestra.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.96,0:01:31.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.32,0:01:35.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nodame also wants to perform a concerto in an orchestra
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.54,0:01:37.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Milch, please let me do it too!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.10,0:01:39.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nodame-chan,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.57,0:01:43.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,just as you are now, it's impossible!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.72,0:01:47.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,unless you face music face to face more,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.72,0:01:51.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,you won't be able to enjoy music from your heart
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.14,0:01:54.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nodame is enjoying it...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.57,0:01:57.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why did you say such a thing?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.65,0:02:03.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, it's time already
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.32,0:02:05.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I have to go.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.99,0:02:07.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Milch....
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.07,0:02:14.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait, Milch!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.95,0:02:16.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nodame-chan...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.35,0:02:22.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,don't forget to lock your door
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.83,0:02:40.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A dream?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.68,0:03:01.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Good morning, Chiaki!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.25,0:03:05.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I.......
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.06,0:03:07.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't you remember?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.74,0:03:12.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No mistake, after that School Festival,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.82,0:03:14.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I was dragged around by Maestro to...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.02,0:03:15.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ginza,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.65,0:03:18.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kyoto,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.50,0:03:21.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and onsen (hot spring)...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.70,0:03:24.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,for three days and three nights.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.31,0:03:30.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yesterday, again we went drinking in Roppongi,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.59,0:03:34.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,that way, I ended up in Maestro's Hotel...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.79,0:03:39.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.65,0:03:41.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Earlier I took him to Narita
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.88,0:03:44.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,because if he changed his mind and said\Nhe wanted to remain in Japan, it won't be good.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.26,0:03:47.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm still here to settle the remaining bill,\Nand to deliver this....
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.77,0:03:48.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Dearest Chiaki"
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.77,0:03:49.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.30,0:03:50.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,From Maestro for Chiaki
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.51,0:03:57.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Chiaki, I have something to ask you.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.20,0:04:00.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please send to Germany
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.42,0:04:02.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,the photo book of Mami Nagaoka
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.02,0:04:04.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,which will be released in December
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.12,0:04:07.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oi!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.87,0:04:08.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Good bye
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.70,0:04:09.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.23,0:04:15.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please convey my gratitude to Maestro....for now.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.96,0:04:16.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll convey it to him
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.18,0:04:19.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And from me to you too
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.13,0:04:20.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.78,0:04:25.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It has been a long time since I saw him\Nconducting so happily
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.33,0:04:27.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.63,0:04:29.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's meet again some day!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.49,0:04:35.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This way....Stresemann went back to his country
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.35,0:04:40.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This time....he really...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.70,0:04:44.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,without mistake.....went home.\N"Stresemann really returned home"
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.47,0:04:49.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then...the time will soon come,\Ncompelling us who are left behind...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.81,0:04:52.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,to choose the road\Nwe are supposed to walk on...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.45,0:04:56.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hmmh....I haven't got any job offer yet...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.81,0:04:57.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Me neither....
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.55,0:05:00.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It felt like a blow after playing so much
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.46,0:05:02.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But it was fun, wasn't it? S-Oke.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.46,0:05:08.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, just when I thought we couldn't participate\Neven once in an Oke after 4 years in the Academy,\Nyet at the very last we managed to. It's good, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.62,0:05:12.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Talking about it, S-Oke has not yet held a\Nclosing party, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.21,0:05:15.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In that case, let's hold a drinking party!\N"Disband Party"!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.77,0:05:18.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait a minute!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.24,0:05:20.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come on, what are you talking, guys?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.60,0:05:23.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why did you talk as if S-Oke is just a\Nmemory of a long long past?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.06,0:05:26.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I have no intention of making it end yet!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.06,0:05:27.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,OK?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.68,0:05:29.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mine-kun!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.94,0:05:32.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I want to do it too!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.92,0:05:33.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sakura!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.02,0:05:38.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yosh, okay shall we continue it?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.64,0:05:39.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, let's!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.44,0:05:40.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Right??
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.47,0:05:42.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That is S-Oke! Right?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.81,0:05:44.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh no! I have an interview in the afternoon!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.52,0:05:45.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I have an Introductory Meeting!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.58,0:05:46.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,See you...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.41,0:05:48.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait...what are you suddenly up to, everybody?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.30,0:05:50.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oi, all of you, what do you want to be? Oi!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.10,0:05:51.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Chiaki-Sama!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.55,0:05:52.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Chiaki!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.38,0:05:53.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Long time no see!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.03,0:05:54.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.90,0:05:55.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mine!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.02,0:05:58.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you still angry that Chiaki was in A-Oke?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.50,0:06:00.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not angry!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.04,0:06:03.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I am....
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.31,0:06:05.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Aaahhh...I was impressed....
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.92,0:06:10.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's...it's....it's the first time I was impressed,\Nother than to my own performance!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.73,0:06:12.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,As expected, you are really my best friend!!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.96,0:06:15.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? Since when did I become your best friend?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.09,0:06:18.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Um....I have a suggestion, if you don't mind....
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.05,0:06:18.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.61,0:06:19.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ehhh??
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.69,0:06:22.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Didn't Chiaki-Senpai come together with Nodame?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.20,0:06:22.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.94,0:06:26.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Since the School Festival, Nodame-chan has\Nnever come to school.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.47,0:06:27.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nodame?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.94,0:06:38.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hello?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.52,0:06:42.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.09,0:06:43.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.03,0:06:48.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Publishing Editor Department\NKawano Keeko
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.47,0:06:51.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ehh, so this is the restaurant Chiaki-kun often goes
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.85,0:06:54.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Somehow it's different from his image
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.57,0:06:55.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Welcome!!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.08,0:06:56.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What would you like to have?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.92,0:06:58.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Clubhouse sandwich and expresso coffee, please
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.86,0:07:00.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Eh?? Sandwich in a Chinese restaurant?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.70,0:07:01.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sure!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.79,0:07:03.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Eh?? There's sandwich here??
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.32,0:07:07.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now, what is it that a music magazine writer\Nwants to talk to me about?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.43,0:07:09.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh! Sorry to say it late...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.54,0:07:12.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm Sakuma Manabu, a music critic.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.92,0:07:14.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Music Critic\NSakuma Manabu
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.22,0:07:17.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In fact Sakuma-san is writing serial articles\Nfor my magazine Classic Life
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.34,0:07:19.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but for next month's article, we asked him\Nto write about Chiaki-kun!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.88,0:07:20.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.53,0:07:23.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dream Color Classic Serial Article\N50th Anniversary
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.81,0:07:25.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Special bonus:
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.51,0:07:27.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,With Pin-up!!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.14,0:07:32.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry for not asking you first!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.01,0:07:36.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But earlier we got permission from Stresemann to\Ntake photos, and he also said please take care of my pupil
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.95,0:07:39.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,See, they are good photos, aren't they?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.27,0:07:39.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Jiijii!!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.98,0:07:41.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please read my part too.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.63,0:07:49.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Reaching the fathomless bottom of a deep ravine\Nis the illuminating light of the piano prelude"
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.35,0:07:50.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"I took a peek into that light...."
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.87,0:07:53.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Aaahhh, beautiful Rachmaninoff piece...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.27,0:07:55.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sakuma-san became your great fan!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.34,0:08:01.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Me too! Since I saw your conducting at school,\NI've been always watching you!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.00,0:08:01.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.49,0:08:03.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Me too, next time I certainly want to see your conducting!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.31,0:08:03.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.75,0:08:05.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Chiaki-kun, after you graduate, you're going\Nto go abroad, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.62,0:08:06.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.12,0:08:08.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Of course as Stresemann's pupil!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.55,0:08:10.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you going to take part in\NConducting Competition over there?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.72,0:08:11.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please wait a minute!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.06,0:08:13.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I have no intention of continuing to Graduate School...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.94,0:08:15.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What a stupid idea!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.88,0:08:19.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It came!!!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.75,0:08:22.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In this vast blue sky far over there,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.07,0:08:24.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,aspiring for the shining sun,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.80,0:08:28.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,spread your snowy white big wings
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.02,0:08:31.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,which have been sheltering\Nthe soul of the sublime music in you,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.13,0:08:33.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,it's time to FLY up for your new journey!!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.07,0:08:33.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Haaa???
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.84,0:08:36.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Why don't you study abroad?" that's what he's saying.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.34,0:08:40.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I.....
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.85,0:08:42.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,CANNOT FLY, YOU KNOW!!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.48,0:08:45.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In this vast ocean far over there,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.17,0:08:47.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,the greatest treasure of Arts
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.40,0:08:49.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,is smiling at you,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.93,0:08:50.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,why didn't you start rowing your boat?\Nis smiling at you,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.28,0:08:52.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,why didn't you start rowing your boat?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.39,0:08:55.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"You'd have a good record of winning competitions abroad."
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.38,0:08:56.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,that's what he's saying.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.08,0:09:00.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I CANNOT ROW A BOAT, YOU KNOW!!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.22,0:09:02.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Neee, why won't you go abroad?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.80,0:09:06.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When you have such a talent,\Nand you have an amazing Master too!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.74,0:09:07.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why??
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.33,0:09:11.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Remaining in Japan, what do you actually intend to do?!!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.71,0:09:13.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wherever I am....whatever I'm doing...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.85,0:09:14.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,IS NONE OF YOUR BUSINESS!!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.66,0:09:17.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You have no right to worry about me!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.16,0:09:19.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Leave me alone!!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.73,0:09:21.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh Chiaki-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.15,0:09:25.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Your sandwich....I specially put pickles in it!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.18,0:09:27.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please wrap it up, I'll pick it up later!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.23,0:09:27.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay!!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.26,0:09:30.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why??
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.58,0:09:34.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Once, God did not forgive Icarus,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.64,0:09:36.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but even God, if He is shown the music you perform,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.69,0:09:40.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He'll probably give you Love, Grace, and Blessing....
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.31,0:09:44.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe your poems made him upset?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.25,0:09:45.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Your orders please?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.89,0:10:00.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.33,0:10:02.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tagaya-san,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.44,0:10:04.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't break the lines in such small parts
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.79,0:10:06.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please express more insecure feeling!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.13,0:10:07.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hai
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.91,0:10:09.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Earlier you heard how Suganuma-san sang, didn't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.07,0:10:12.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sing like that, with rich emotion!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.18,0:10:14.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Again, Suganuma?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.09,0:10:18.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You have a very beautiful voice, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.00,0:10:19.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,it's as if you can't get through one thing...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.55,0:10:24.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you plan to continue to Graduate School\Nand to sing, you have to get through this wall...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.56,0:10:30.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hmph....no timpani....
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.39,0:10:32.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Japan Metropolitan Philharmony"\NRecruitment: Violin
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.02,0:10:32.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Audition for Oboe"
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.91,0:10:33.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Looking for Oboe Player"
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.36,0:10:35.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Masumi-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.88,0:10:37.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, Kiyora!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.71,0:10:39.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,As I expected, you're going to apply\Nto a Professional Orchestra?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.32,0:10:44.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, but at the time there's no\Nrecruitment for timpani player at all....
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.32,0:10:47.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's really a tough world!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.39,0:10:52.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ne, about Chiaki-kun, what's he going\Nto do after graduation?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.71,0:10:55.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why on earth did you ask about Chiaki-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.60,0:10:56.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,WHAT IS IN YOUR MIND?!!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.04,0:11:01.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No wories! After the outcome is fixed, I'll tell\NMasumi-chan too.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.95,0:11:02.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.04,0:11:06.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Eh, Chiaki?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.24,0:11:11.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, but he hasn't shown up after saying\Nthat he would pick it up
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.48,0:11:13.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is that why you came to the school to deliver it?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.47,0:11:15.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Of course!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.90,0:11:17.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Chiaki-san is your best friend, isn't he?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.85,0:11:19.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, yes.....
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.52,0:11:20.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let me deliver it....
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.10,0:11:24.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll deliver it!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.73,0:11:33.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In the end, I....
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.15,0:11:35.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,am stuck at the same place again.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.38,0:11:38.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even if I have conducted in student orchestra...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.34,0:11:41.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,even if I have performed a concerto with Stresemann...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.49,0:11:45.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why won't you go abroad??
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.26,0:11:48.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When you have such a talent!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.30,0:12:09.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Saiko
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.58,0:12:12.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Noda"
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.96,0:12:27.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But Nodame-chan, in your condition now,\Nyou can't be together with Chiaki
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.94,0:12:29.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,can't be together\Ncan't be together
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.27,0:12:57.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nodame Cantabile\NLesson 6
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.32,0:13:08.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,http://s-projects.org
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.46,0:13:15.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't need it, you didn't have to deliver it
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.17,0:13:16.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's that attitude?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.09,0:13:18.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Recently you're so cold!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.04,0:13:20.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you for delivering it!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.88,0:13:24.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Right! They asked me to, that's why I\Nhad no choice but to deliver it!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.59,0:13:34.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,By the way, I saw it....\NShinichi's Concert
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.81,0:13:37.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It was extremely good
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.48,0:13:39.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But....
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.37,0:13:41.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,somehow you seem to have\Ngone far away, suddenly...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.79,0:13:44.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's not true
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.59,0:13:49.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You too, in these four years you have progressed\Nto sing quite well
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.00,0:13:51.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Really??
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.02,0:13:55.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Especially the low register can come out well now
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.67,0:13:59.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But one thing still cannot come through
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.32,0:14:01.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Though you have technique,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.80,0:14:03.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,your acting ability is lacking....
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.21,0:14:05.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,whatever you sing, it's always one pattern that\Nit becomes boring
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.87,0:14:08.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,if you let out your malicious\Ncharacter more,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.01,0:14:11.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,perhaps the song you're singing\Nwould also have some breadth?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.75,0:14:13.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll go to konbini and will be back soon
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.73,0:14:15.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you go home, you can leave the door unlocked as it is
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.70,0:14:20.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't know he's such a jerk!!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.45,0:14:27.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Noda"
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.79,0:14:38.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Shubi Gakuen Music High School"\NYear 2002 Graduation Album
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.86,0:14:44.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Rather than worrying about me...always music, music...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.99,0:14:48.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He never changes...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.18,0:14:57.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If I quit music...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.73,0:15:03.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,will we be able to stay together?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.62,0:15:15.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Saiko!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.50,0:15:20.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So she's gone home
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.39,0:15:27.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Eeek!!!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.09,0:15:30.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Be careful, lock your door...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.88,0:15:32.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No....Nodame??
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.09,0:15:34.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, Nodame...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.55,0:15:37.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So you're still in Costume playing....
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.34,0:15:38.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, I'm not
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.05,0:15:41.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Senpai!!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.36,0:15:44.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please let Nodame play piano concerto\Nin an orchestra too!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.25,0:15:45.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.32,0:15:49.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nodame also wants to practice\Nthe piece Senpai performed!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.30,0:15:52.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nodame also wants to play that piece!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.43,0:15:59.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Senpai, I want to play... piano....
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.77,0:16:01.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You stink!!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.22,0:16:02.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.60,0:16:05.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You....for how many days haven't you taken a bath?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.77,0:16:08.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How many days? What day is today?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.79,0:16:08.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Go take a bath now!\NHow many days? What day is today?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.88,0:16:10.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Go take a bath now!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.51,0:16:11.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The gas....
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.32,0:16:12.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Again??
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.88,0:16:14.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,OK, OK, take a bath in my house!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.66,0:16:16.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But what about the clothes to change...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.31,0:16:20.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Here! This is the clothes you left here!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.45,0:16:23.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That female!!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.01,0:16:25.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who is she?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.38,0:16:32.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That girl...after she listened to my concerto,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.30,0:16:35.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,she keeps practising after that?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.60,0:16:37.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Until she became like that...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.64,0:16:39.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Here, eat it!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.23,0:16:41.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I have no appetite
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.51,0:16:44.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,OK, eat it!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.68,0:16:45.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Gyabo!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.42,0:16:48.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Anyway, eat it!!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.93,0:16:51.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Concerto first...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.55,0:16:53.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's impossible for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.09,0:16:55.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.67,0:16:57.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You never see the score, playing it your own way,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.98,0:16:59.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,composing your own song!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.18,0:17:00.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How could the orchestra possibly harmonize with you?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.99,0:17:06.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Although Nodame do not see the score,\NI have heard Rachmaninoff a few times, I know it
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.49,0:17:09.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Moreover, Senpai's piano sound...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.13,0:17:13.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,still remains in my ears...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.94,0:17:19.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nodame also wants to play...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.48,0:17:22.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,the way you did.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.16,0:17:25.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nodame...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.91,0:17:28.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yosh!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.61,0:17:31.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you want to do it that much,\Nokay let me hear it.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.30,0:17:32.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.66,0:17:33.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Your Rachmaninoff!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.12,0:17:35.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go to the school
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.18,0:17:37.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's better to have two pianos!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.68,0:17:38.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Senpai!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.68,0:17:46.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go home!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.86,0:17:48.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,One more song, one more song!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.67,0:17:49.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ehhhhh??
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.57,0:17:52.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you're just having fun playing,\Nwould you let us have a turn?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.15,0:17:52.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ha--hai!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.08,0:17:54.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My pleasure!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.85,0:17:56.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nodame?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.77,0:17:58.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.15,0:18:03.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll play the part of the Oke,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.27,0:18:05.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and you play as usual
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.64,0:18:07.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Imagine there's an Oke here.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.24,0:18:11.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.79,0:18:16.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Alright.....you can start whenever you like.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.69,0:18:36.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The first pianissimo is played as fortessimo?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.03,0:18:38.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What piece is this?!!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.20,0:18:47.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,On top of that, it's fast!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.01,0:18:49.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You can play this piece at this tempo??
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.00,0:18:56.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Rachmaninoff Piano Concerto No 2?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.25,0:18:57.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is it Chiaki-sama who's playing it?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.99,0:19:03.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Eh...Chiaki-sama is accompanying it...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.19,0:19:04.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It can't be!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.35,0:19:06.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So the one playing is.....Nodame??
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.20,0:19:13.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There are too many sounds....
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.26,0:19:16.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,As expected, you're composing, aren't you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.60,0:19:26.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Moreover, she's already at it from the start.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.67,0:19:29.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She's just playing it on impulse.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.03,0:19:34.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It won't be!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.41,0:19:36.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is not a Concerto.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.85,0:19:38.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shall I stop it?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.58,0:19:46.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dammit!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.66,0:19:49.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll harmonize with you!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.49,0:19:51.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Listen to my sound!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.29,0:20:03.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oi!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.39,0:20:05.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you doing this late?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.34,0:20:07.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All of you!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.55,0:20:07.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come on!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.03,0:20:09.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Or I'll drop you off.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.25,0:20:35.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Amazing!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.84,0:20:37.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,As I thought, aren't they dating?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.13,0:20:38.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Those two.....
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.90,0:20:39.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ehhh?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.66,0:20:44.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, they're always together...if they were not,\Nhow could they possibly play like that....
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.35,0:20:47.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,despite Nodame playing it very sloppily,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.05,0:20:50.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,perhaps those two have matching minds...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.61,0:20:53.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even so, I didn't know Nodame could play that well
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.35,0:21:15.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's enough....
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.54,0:21:17.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop it....
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.01,0:21:21.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's enough.....
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.50,0:21:42.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oi, Nodame!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.18,0:21:44.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's time to go home!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.61,0:21:49.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oi!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.84,0:22:00.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This girl....
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.23,0:22:02.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,what should I do with her?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.46,0:22:08.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Here, from today, practice the Concerto.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.53,0:22:10.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But I already played the Concerto.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.46,0:22:11.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.40,0:22:13.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Senpai accompanied me, didn't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.00,0:22:16.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Already played it?\NBut you said you wanted to play it in an orchestra
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.79,0:22:20.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Senpai's piano was like a real orchestra!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.44,0:22:22.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I felt very good...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.96,0:22:24.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nodame is very satisfied!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.53,0:22:27.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Really thank you very much!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.15,0:22:28.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I was extremely happy!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.53,0:22:32.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're satisfied with such a performance?\NIs that enough?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.33,0:22:33.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nodame
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.33,0:22:36.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ara! You're here, Nodame-chan?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.53,0:22:37.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Aaaa, Masumi-chan!!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.72,0:22:41.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Chiaki! Look at this!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.83,0:22:43.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Voila! We got job offer!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.88,0:22:45.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Job Offer Notification"
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.53,0:22:46.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Congratulations!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.44,0:22:49.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Our music company has also been decided.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.97,0:22:54.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,While working at the company we'll continue\Ntaking lessons, while hoping we can make a professional debut...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.08,0:22:56.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's great!!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.33,0:22:58.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,As for me, I'm to take over my family's bakery
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.83,0:23:02.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Me too, I'm going to help my family's Inn\Nin my hometown. Please come and visit, everyone!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.05,0:23:06.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ne, ne, what are you going to do, Shizuka-chan?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.09,0:23:13.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Waaaaahhh!!!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.65,0:23:15.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shizuka-chan is going to get married?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.53,0:23:25.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Although I'm glad for them, I will feel lonely...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.37,0:23:33.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I envy Shizuka-chan....getting married....
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.61,0:23:37.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nodame wants to graduate and get married at\Nthe same time....
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.56,0:23:39.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes do it....with a person from the same planet as yours!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.78,0:23:42.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Naturally Chiaki-Senpai will continue to\Nthe Graduate School, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.94,0:23:47.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's great! There are so many people either\Ngoing to study abroad or return to their home!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:47.20,0:23:48.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nodame, shut up!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.65,0:23:50.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you're not practicing, get out!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.33,0:23:51.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:52.29,0:23:54.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ack! Mine-kun, what's up?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:55.70,0:23:56.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Chiaki...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.05,0:24:00.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I have been thinking...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:01.47,0:24:02.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Can we continue S-Oke?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:02.92,0:24:03.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:04.05,0:24:05.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's a good idea!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:05.31,0:24:07.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Right? Moreover third year students Sakura\Nand me can continue...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:08.10,0:24:12.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you do it, Masumi-chan will do it too...\Nand the others will find time in their works to get together...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:12.53,0:24:13.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop joking around!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:13.57,0:24:14.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:14.98,0:24:17.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't have time to entertain such unrealistic talk!!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:18.07,0:24:19.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where is it unrealistic??
Dialogue: 0,0:24:19.77,0:24:21.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Amateur Oke, whatever Oke, there are so many Oke, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:22.68,0:24:24.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If we wish to continue, we can continue, can't we?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:25.05,0:24:27.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,With you becoming the Conductor,\Nall of us can gather more people...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:27.28,0:24:28.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And then?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:29.71,0:24:30.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,With you as the Concert Master,
Dialogue: 0,0:24:30.99,0:24:32.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and that fuzzy-fuzzy Sakura,
Dialogue: 0,0:24:32.09,0:24:33.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,you expect me to be the Conductor??
Dialogue: 0,0:24:33.34,0:24:35.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you intend to do with that\N"we-are-all-friends" play-acting?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:36.42,0:24:38.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Like aspiring to become a professional Oke?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:38.38,0:24:39.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Gimme a break!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:39.88,0:24:41.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then what are Chiaki going to do from now?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:41.85,0:24:43.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is there a place you can conduct?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:43.80,0:24:44.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:44.98,0:24:47.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Remaining in Japan, what do you actually intend to do?!!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:50.35,0:24:51.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Didn't you want to be a Conductor?!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:55.01,0:24:56.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Idiot Chiaki!!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:59.44,0:25:00.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This person too, that person too....
Dialogue: 0,0:25:01.49,0:25:02.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who needs your meddling!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:03.20,0:25:04.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Senpai, what are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:05.67,0:25:06.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What? Shopping for dinner!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:08.10,0:25:09.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Fish meat....
Dialogue: 0,0:25:09.48,0:25:10.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Deer meat...
Dialogue: 0,0:25:11.30,0:25:12.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Bear meat....
Dialogue: 0,0:25:13.62,0:25:14.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Bullying?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:19.24,0:25:21.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Kangaroo Meat"
Dialogue: 0,0:25:21.68,0:25:24.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Senpai, today Nodame will treat you!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:27.13,0:25:29.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,(this is kaiten/turning-around sushi, cheap)
Dialogue: 0,0:25:29.80,0:25:31.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,(3000 yen!)
Dialogue: 0,0:25:33.16,0:25:36.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, please help yourself!\NToday I'll treat you to sushi!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:37.37,0:25:39.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, here comes the egg....the egg...\N(cheapest)
Dialogue: 0,0:25:40.87,0:25:42.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What Senpai likes hasn't come round yet?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:43.66,0:25:44.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dammit!!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:45.09,0:25:46.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why are the sushi turning around?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:47.08,0:25:50.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,(which shows he's never been to kaiten sushi,\Nbut only to bar sushi, which is EXPENSIVE)
Dialogue: 0,0:25:50.68,0:25:51.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,(sea urchin, gold plate price=400 yen)
Dialogue: 0,0:25:52.23,0:25:53.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mukyaaa!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:53.26,0:25:55.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sea urchin?? Suddenly sea urchin??
Dialogue: 0,0:25:55.16,0:25:57.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Senpai, that's gold plate! 400 yen!!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:59.02,0:26:02.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's decided in the market that a student\Nshould only take the 100-yen white plates....
Dialogue: 0,0:26:03.09,0:26:04.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Humph!! Just so so!\N(=which shows he only eats high grade sea urchin!)
Dialogue: 0,0:26:05.14,0:26:07.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Here! Hmh! I'll give them to you!!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:08.29,0:26:09.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,These too, I'll give them to you!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:09.30,0:26:10.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Gyabo!!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:10.75,0:26:12.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why did you leave the rice??
Dialogue: 0,0:26:13.71,0:26:15.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You just eat the sashimi toppings??
Dialogue: 0,0:26:16.11,0:26:18.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ohhh....again it's gold plate!\N(abalone, 400yen)
Dialogue: 0,0:26:18.33,0:26:21.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nodame also wants to eat sashimi with rice....
Dialogue: 0,0:26:21.84,0:26:22.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, here they are!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:23.29,0:26:23.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Gari sushi"!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:23.94,0:26:26.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,(no such thing! He just put the FREE ginger pickles,\Nor "gari", on the rice!!)
Dialogue: 0,0:26:26.41,0:26:28.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,MUKYAAAAAAAAAAAAAAA!!!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:28.76,0:26:30.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Senpai is weird! No common sense!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:30.81,0:26:32.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Surely I'm NOT going to treat you anymore!!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:32.76,0:26:35.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What treat? In the end I was the one paying!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:35.76,0:26:38.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If one has only 3000 yen, will she normally\Nenter a sushi shop?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:38.25,0:26:40.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Usually that's always enough for a\Nkaiten sushi!!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:41.73,0:26:45.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Senpai seems strange, so Nodame....
Dialogue: 0,0:26:46.94,0:26:47.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Could it be...
Dialogue: 0,0:26:48.72,0:26:50.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,that even Nodame is worried about me?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:51.81,0:26:53.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's this....everybody's worrying about me...
Dialogue: 0,0:26:56.18,0:26:57.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Senpai?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:57.31,0:26:59.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Someone like Nodame, it's not your place to worry about others
Dialogue: 0,0:27:00.47,0:27:01.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You too, next year you'll be a fourth-year student!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:02.49,0:27:03.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you going to do after that?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:04.50,0:27:05.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What am I going to do?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:06.32,0:27:09.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,After graduating, Nodame intends to be a\Nkindergarten teacher
Dialogue: 0,0:27:12.34,0:27:13.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So you were serious....
Dialogue: 0,0:27:13.79,0:27:14.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:14.74,0:27:18.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's why next year I'll be busy with\Nsuch things like training in the field of education...
Dialogue: 0,0:27:19.63,0:27:20.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:21.49,0:27:24.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When I thought you had become a little\Nbit more serious about piano...
Dialogue: 0,0:27:25.04,0:27:27.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even though you play sloppily....\Nyou can play that well!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:28.13,0:27:29.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why didn't you aim higher?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:32.37,0:27:33.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:33.40,0:27:35.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why won't you go abroad?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:35.34,0:27:37.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When you have such a talent!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:38.43,0:27:40.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just as I think about Nodame....
Dialogue: 0,0:27:41.24,0:27:44.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,if everyone also thinks about me...
Dialogue: 0,0:27:45.14,0:27:46.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,that's something to be grateful for....
Dialogue: 0,0:27:46.84,0:27:48.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,perhaps it's an honor...
Dialogue: 0,0:27:50.51,0:27:53.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Senpai....yes as I thought, you're strange...
Dialogue: 0,0:27:55.52,0:27:59.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's not a problem of not being able to go\Nabroad anymore...now
Dialogue: 0,0:28:00.61,0:28:01.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes...
Dialogue: 0,0:28:02.08,0:28:03.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why??
Dialogue: 0,0:28:03.38,0:28:06.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Remaining in Japan, what do you actually intend to do?!!
Dialogue: 0,0:28:06.54,0:28:07.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That is the problem.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:14.50,0:28:15.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Senpai....
Dialogue: 0,0:28:15.49,0:28:16.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Cut it out!!
Dialogue: 0,0:28:17.24,0:28:17.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Iyaaan....
Dialogue: 0,0:28:19.19,0:28:20.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,GIMME A BREAK!!
Dialogue: 0,0:28:23.51,0:28:24.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Too near!!
Dialogue: 0,0:28:24.63,0:28:25.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Chiaki!
Dialogue: 0,0:28:26.16,0:28:27.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not going to give up!
Dialogue: 0,0:28:28.24,0:28:29.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Too persistent!!
Dialogue: 0,0:28:30.53,0:28:31.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Chiaki-kun!
Dialogue: 0,0:28:31.92,0:28:34.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Good! I had been looking for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:34.42,0:28:35.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:44.41,0:28:46.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Eh? You're going to Graduate School too?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:47.06,0:28:49.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Actually I planned to return to Vienna soon
Dialogue: 0,0:28:50.41,0:28:54.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but the teacher who used to guide me over there\Nwill be busy for a while doing his own tour...
Dialogue: 0,0:28:55.13,0:28:59.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, it's a good chance....I'm thinking of\Nparticipating in competitions here in Japan
Dialogue: 0,0:29:00.02,0:29:01.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Eeh.....
Dialogue: 0,0:29:01.88,0:29:03.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That, and....
Dialogue: 0,0:29:04.16,0:29:05.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,there's one more thing I want to do....
Dialogue: 0,0:29:07.73,0:29:10.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I want to make an orchestra....with Chiaki-kun
Dialogue: 0,0:29:11.53,0:29:12.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:12.38,0:29:13.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:13.13,0:29:17.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Honestly, until now I had had no interest\Nin student orchestra...
Dialogue: 0,0:29:19.10,0:29:20.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,However....
Dialogue: 0,0:29:20.47,0:29:22.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,my performing with Stresemann in A-Oke\Nwas an incentive...
Dialogue: 0,0:29:24.12,0:29:27.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,on top of that, Chiaki-kun's conducting in\Nthe periodical public performance was also...
Dialogue: 0,0:29:28.15,0:29:29.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,quite an incentive.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:32.32,0:29:35.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Won't you make an orchestra with me,\Nand perform together?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:35.80,0:29:36.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I will
Dialogue: 0,0:29:36.81,0:29:37.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Immediate answer??
Dialogue: 0,0:29:38.41,0:29:40.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No....though I want to do it...but
Dialogue: 0,0:29:41.24,0:29:42.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If it's about the members of the orchestra,\Nthere's no need to worry
Dialogue: 0,0:29:43.77,0:29:48.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Actually I have talked with some students from\Nother Academies whom I got to know from a\NMusic Festival in Vienna
Dialogue: 0,0:29:49.28,0:29:50.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All are excellent students
Dialogue: 0,0:29:51.15,0:29:54.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,For example Kikuchi-kun from Toukoku Music Academy,\Nwho won First Prize in Austria International Competition
Dialogue: 0,0:29:55.42,0:29:56.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kikuchi...who plays cello?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:57.73,0:29:58.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've heard of him from rumors!
Dialogue: 0,0:29:59.12,0:30:00.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's also in Japan now
Dialogue: 0,0:30:00.54,0:30:02.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then, Kuroki-kun from Morimichi Academy
Dialogue: 0,0:30:03.57,0:30:04.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've heard of him too
Dialogue: 0,0:30:06.31,0:30:09.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,As to the others...there are some who are still\Nstudying abroad, or residing in Kansai....
Dialogue: 0,0:30:10.20,0:30:12.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If Chiaki-kun invite them, I think\Nthey'll come to gather here
Dialogue: 0,0:30:13.20,0:30:14.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? Me?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:15.03,0:30:18.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Of course! Chiaki-kun is a Superstar now!
Dialogue: 0,0:30:18.92,0:30:19.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Haaa?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:20.10,0:30:21.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dream Color Classic, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:28.14,0:30:29.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:30:38.58,0:30:39.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,See you later.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:39.34,0:30:40.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,OK.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:46.86,0:30:47.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Chiaki!
Dialogue: 0,0:30:48.70,0:30:49.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Geh!!
Dialogue: 0,0:30:54.57,0:30:56.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please let me enter your Oke too!
Dialogue: 0,0:30:56.62,0:30:57.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:57.33,0:30:59.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If it's for Chiaki's Oke, I'll do anything!
Dialogue: 0,0:31:04.64,0:31:06.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In that case, show me you can enter A-Oke\Nin your next exam!
Dialogue: 0,0:31:07.57,0:31:08.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then I'll let you in!
Dialogue: 0,0:31:11.16,0:31:11.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Alright!!
Dialogue: 0,0:31:12.28,0:31:13.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Alright! Alright!
Dialogue: 0,0:31:13.53,0:31:16.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I did it....alrighttttt....
Dialogue: 0,0:31:21.41,0:31:23.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Senpai is going to make an orchestra, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:25.87,0:31:26.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:27.70,0:31:29.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Today is reserved for\NMomogaoka Music Academy's\NS-Oke Group"
Dialogue: 0,0:31:29.83,0:31:31.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"S-Oke Disband Party"
Dialogue: 0,0:31:31.86,0:31:38.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I, Mine Ryutaro, would like to ask you to drink a toast\Nfor the job offers for the fourth year students,\Nand for the safe disbanding of S-Oke!
Dialogue: 0,0:31:38.85,0:31:40.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, why is that?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:41.22,0:31:44.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Didn't you say you wanted to continue S-Oke, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:44.63,0:31:47.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,KANPAI!!!!
Dialogue: 0,0:31:47.69,0:31:49.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kanpai!!!
Dialogue: 0,0:31:51.17,0:31:54.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mascot!! Beer! Beer! Serve it around!
Dialogue: 0,0:31:54.17,0:31:55.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hai! Masumi-chan, here's more beer
Dialogue: 0,0:31:57.36,0:31:58.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Here's for you!
Dialogue: 0,0:31:58.75,0:32:00.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, it hurts...
Dialogue: 0,0:32:00.29,0:32:02.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You! Don't you dare to overdo it, OK!
Dialogue: 0,0:32:02.80,0:32:03.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What about?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:04.19,0:32:06.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't know Chiaki-Sama's going to\Ncontinue to Graduate School!
Dialogue: 0,0:32:07.71,0:32:11.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I thought Chiaki-Sama would certainly go to study abroad
Dialogue: 0,0:32:12.43,0:32:15.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but that he's going to remain in Japan makes me happy....
Dialogue: 0,0:32:15.87,0:32:17.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Could it be because there's Nodame here?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:18.56,0:32:19.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll kill you!
Dialogue: 0,0:32:19.33,0:32:22.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah! As Masumi-chan's job is not decided yet,
Dialogue: 0,0:32:22.63,0:32:24.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,what about repeating for one year at school?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:24.57,0:32:26.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll certainly kill you!
Dialogue: 0,0:32:37.92,0:32:40.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Today, I must tell Kaoru-chan about my feeling...
Dialogue: 0,0:32:47.68,0:32:48.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kaoru-chan....I......
Dialogue: 0,0:32:49.56,0:32:52.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's my turn to pour Chiaki-Sama's beer now!
Dialogue: 0,0:32:52.37,0:32:53.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, stop it!
Dialogue: 0,0:32:53.67,0:32:55.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's my turn! It's my turn!
Dialogue: 0,0:32:55.56,0:32:56.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That Chiaki!
Dialogue: 0,0:32:57.22,0:32:59.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Till the very end....
Dialogue: 0,0:32:59.74,0:33:03.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey.....I have a good idea....
Dialogue: 0,0:33:04.65,0:33:05.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:05.30,0:33:06.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Heheeheee...
Dialogue: 0,0:33:06.39,0:33:08.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you doing? Oi!
Dialogue: 0,0:33:08.83,0:33:12.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's love ......
Dialogue: 0,0:33:12.71,0:33:17.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...vacation
Dialogue: 0,0:33:17.63,0:33:20.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oi! Kaoruuuuu!!
Dialogue: 0,0:33:22.32,0:33:24.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,(heart mark)
Dialogue: 0,0:33:28.90,0:33:31.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Chijou no Hoshi" (The Stars above The Earth)\NLyrics by Nakajima Miyuki
Dialogue: 0,0:33:31.47,0:33:32.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who put in this song??
Dialogue: 0,0:33:32.82,0:33:33.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Chiaki!
Dialogue: 0,0:33:33.79,0:33:35.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Chiaki-kun's going to sing this song!
Dialogue: 0,0:33:35.90,0:33:36.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:36.64,0:33:38.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Chiaki-Sama singing karaoke??
Dialogue: 0,0:33:38.10,0:33:38.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Incredible!
Dialogue: 0,0:33:40.55,0:33:42.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How is it, the girls won't want to see it, will they?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:42.50,0:33:44.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Chiaki Shinichi crying out Nakajima\NMiyuki's song passionately!
Dialogue: 0,0:33:44.37,0:33:47.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's a punishment for what he did until now!\NLet's make him feel totally ashamed!
Dialogue: 0,0:33:47.58,0:33:49.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Heeheeheeee.....
Dialogue: 0,0:33:49.52,0:33:50.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I know this song!
Dialogue: 0,0:33:55.59,0:33:56.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait a minute!!!
Dialogue: 0,0:33:57.23,0:33:58.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is Ore-Sama's theme song!!\N(Ore-Sama=I )
Dialogue: 0,0:33:58.99,0:33:59.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,OK
Dialogue: 0,0:34:03.06,0:34:03.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Kaze no...."
Dialogue: 0,0:34:03.91,0:34:04.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop it!
Dialogue: 0,0:34:07.55,0:34:10.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ne, ne, there are a lot of S-Oke members gathering there...
Dialogue: 0,0:34:10.60,0:34:15.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Farewell always comes right after happiness...."
Dialogue: 0,0:34:17.01,0:34:18.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Saiko-chan....her character changed!
Dialogue: 0,0:34:19.06,0:34:22.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, it's as if she managed to go through the wall...
Dialogue: 0,0:34:22.33,0:34:23.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Whenever I wake up, I'm...."
Dialogue: 0,0:34:23.39,0:34:25.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...alone!"
Dialogue: 0,0:34:25.33,0:34:25.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,toilet....
Dialogue: 0,0:34:25.95,0:34:26.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,toilet...
Dialogue: 0,0:34:27.41,0:34:29.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,toilet, toilet, toilet...
Dialogue: 0,0:34:29.46,0:34:31.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Aa-ackk! toilet..
Dialogue: 0,0:34:31.89,0:34:33.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,toilet...
Dialogue: 0,0:34:34.25,0:34:35.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Whoops!
Dialogue: 0,0:34:40.03,0:34:42.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ohhh! Tagaya Saiko!
Dialogue: 0,0:34:46.03,0:34:48.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ahhahaha...sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:34:48.58,0:34:51.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Because you called my name without "san",\Nso I did it without thinking....
Dialogue: 0,0:34:56.25,0:34:57.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey....are you alright?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:02.92,0:35:05.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wow....you smell good....
Dialogue: 0,0:35:05.93,0:35:08.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why is Shinichi going out with such a girl like this?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:09.53,0:35:13.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mmm..mmm...hoho...hum..mmmff...
Dialogue: 0,0:35:14.02,0:35:15.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That guy,
Dialogue: 0,0:35:16.02,0:35:17.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,despite this kind of girl, he must have a\Nsoft spot for this...
Dialogue: 0,0:35:18.87,0:35:21.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But, it's not that I have accepted it!
Dialogue: 0,0:35:23.13,0:35:24.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't sleep!!
Dialogue: 0,0:35:28.39,0:35:30.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Taiko Tetsujin"\N(Drum Master)
Dialogue: 0,0:35:30.60,0:35:32.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Heheeeheeehe...
Dialogue: 0,0:35:32.84,0:35:34.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oi, Chiaki!!
Dialogue: 0,0:35:34.40,0:35:35.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come here!
Dialogue: 0,0:35:35.38,0:35:36.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's an interesting game!
Dialogue: 0,0:35:37.30,0:35:38.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Try to play it, it's my treat!
Dialogue: 0,0:35:41.60,0:35:43.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Drum Master?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:43.15,0:35:45.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It'll be easy, isn't it, if you use your\NConductor's sense of rhythm
Dialogue: 0,0:35:45.82,0:35:46.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Here, hold the sticks!
Dialogue: 0,0:35:46.93,0:35:48.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Spread out your legs!
Dialogue: 0,0:35:48.57,0:35:50.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The pose is also important in\Ndetermining the scores!
Dialogue: 0,0:35:50.44,0:35:52.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's a lie....Hehehe...
Dialogue: 0,0:35:53.48,0:35:56.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Everybody! Chiaki's going to beat the drums!!
Dialogue: 0,0:35:56.52,0:35:57.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He'll do it, he'll do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:36:03.32,0:36:05.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Beating the drums strangely,
Dialogue: 0,0:36:05.01,0:36:10.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,we'll make him leave a black stain\Non the white handkerchief\Nin the memory of the Academy's infatuated ladies!
Dialogue: 0,0:36:12.13,0:36:14.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Chijou No Hoshi" (The Stars Above The Earth)
Dialogue: 0,0:36:14.70,0:36:16.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This song again, I know it!
Dialogue: 0,0:36:16.53,0:36:17.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait a minute!!
Dialogue: 0,0:36:21.46,0:36:23.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I told you this is Ore-Sama's theme song....
Dialogue: 0,0:36:25.91,0:36:29.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Chiaki-Sama, all percussions in this world are mine!
Dialogue: 0,0:36:30.29,0:36:30.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,OK
Dialogue: 0,0:36:30.76,0:36:32.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Alright! Let's begin!!
Dialogue: 0,0:36:41.45,0:36:43.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Amazing, Masumi-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:36:44.71,0:36:47.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Today, please listen, Chiaki-Sama!
Dialogue: 0,0:36:48.42,0:36:50.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My feeling for these four years!
Dialogue: 0,0:36:55.71,0:36:56.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This....
Dialogue: 0,0:36:57.77,0:36:58.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,this....
Dialogue: 0,0:36:59.21,0:37:01.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,..sound percussion of love!!
Dialogue: 0,0:37:56.86,0:37:58.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Masumi-chan!\NMasumi-chan!!
Dialogue: 0,0:38:07.34,0:38:10.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,With this I'm not in S-Oke anymore,\Nand graduate from Chiaki-Sama as well!
Dialogue: 0,0:38:22.90,0:38:23.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I....
Dialogue: 0,0:38:25.20,0:38:26.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,am going to make a new Oke.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:29.00,0:38:31.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Though it's not quite right to ask a person\Nwho's aspiring to be a professional...
Dialogue: 0,0:38:33.67,0:38:35.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,it's OK to do it only whenever you can afford the time...
Dialogue: 0,0:38:36.55,0:38:38.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,would you be our timpanist,
Dialogue: 0,0:38:38.61,0:38:39.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Masumi?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:47.08,0:38:48.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,HAI!!!
Dialogue: 0,0:38:59.22,0:38:59.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sakura!
Dialogue: 0,0:39:00.80,0:39:01.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hmm?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:02.47,0:39:03.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,From tomorrow, practice as hard as you can!
Dialogue: 0,0:39:04.63,0:39:05.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:06.28,0:39:07.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Together with me...
Dialogue: 0,0:39:08.62,0:39:09.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,let's get into A-Oke!
Dialogue: 0,0:39:15.95,0:39:20.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't forget us...
Dialogue: 0,0:39:21.87,0:39:24.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,shine forever....
Dialogue: 0,0:39:24.40,0:39:28.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...the legendary Super Orchestra!!
Dialogue: 0,0:39:28.55,0:39:32.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Legend of S-Oke....
Dialogue: 0,0:39:32.37,0:39:36.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Legend of....
Dialogue: 0,0:39:36.71,0:39:38.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Real bad!
Dialogue: 0,0:39:40.92,0:39:41.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hick!
Dialogue: 0,0:39:44.63,0:39:45.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hick!
Dialogue: 0,0:39:48.77,0:39:53.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Bye-bye! Bye-bye!
Dialogue: 0,0:39:55.17,0:39:57.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Bye-bye! Bye-bye!
Dialogue: 0,0:39:59.10,0:40:00.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Bye-bye! Bye-bye!
Dialogue: 0,0:40:00.96,0:40:01.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Bye-bye!
Dialogue: 0,0:40:02.16,0:40:03.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Bye-bye!
Dialogue: 0,0:40:04.78,0:40:05.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hick!
Dialogue: 0,0:40:08.17,0:40:08.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hick!
Dialogue: 0,0:40:12.25,0:40:15.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What had Nodame been doing until now?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:16.40,0:40:17.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Whose shawl is this?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:17.92,0:40:19.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How would I know?!
Dialogue: 0,0:40:19.04,0:40:20.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oi! Let's go to one more drinking place!
Dialogue: 0,0:40:21.11,0:40:22.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Eeehhhhh???
Dialogue: 0,0:40:22.55,0:40:24.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Before that, let's go to a game center first!\NLet's go to a game center!
Dialogue: 0,0:40:25.10,0:40:27.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All game centers must have already been closed!
Dialogue: 0,0:40:28.26,0:40:30.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In that case, let's go to Karaoke!
Dialogue: 0,0:40:30.96,0:40:34.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ehh? Did you really like games and karaoke that much??
Dialogue: 0,0:40:36.51,0:40:37.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,NO, I DON'T LIKE THEM!!
Dialogue: 0,0:40:38.12,0:40:40.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But they always hindered me!!
Dialogue: 0,0:40:43.27,0:40:44.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I must have been a hated person
Dialogue: 0,0:40:45.23,0:40:47.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Senpai, nobody hates you...
Dialogue: 0,0:40:48.12,0:40:50.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...or, they like you with an effort...
Dialogue: 0,0:40:56.21,0:40:57.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I had no choice....
Dialogue: 0,0:40:59.16,0:41:01.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry, sorry, the konbini was quite far...
Dialogue: 0,0:41:01.44,0:41:03.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kaoru-chan, coffee or oolong tea, which one would you...
Dialogue: 0,0:41:10.33,0:41:11.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ssss...sss...synchronized crying!
Dialogue: 0,0:41:12.02,0:41:13.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Chiaki-Sama....
Dialogue: 0,0:41:15.45,0:41:18.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,didn't invite us to his new Oke...
Dialogue: 0,0:41:19.17,0:41:23.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Today a few people asked me to let them\Ninto the new Oke....
Dialogue: 0,0:41:24.19,0:41:25.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but I rejected them.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:28.02,0:41:30.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I also enjoyed being in S-Oke.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:30.35,0:41:32.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Moreover it's the first orchestra I conducted
Dialogue: 0,0:41:32.68,0:41:34.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Though I feel grateful to them,
Dialogue: 0,0:41:36.77,0:41:40.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but for this new Oke, I don't want it to be\Nan extension of S-Oke
Dialogue: 0,0:41:43.70,0:41:46.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I want to make the best orchestra I can
Dialogue: 0,0:41:49.28,0:41:50.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But.....
Dialogue: 0,0:41:51.25,0:41:52.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dammit! That man!
Dialogue: 0,0:41:53.49,0:41:54.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just wait, you'll see!
Dialogue: 0,0:41:55.58,0:41:57.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Certainly we're not going to give up!
Dialogue: 0,0:41:57.89,0:41:58.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,..even so....
Dialogue: 0,0:41:59.70,0:42:01.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,if they look back at me...
Dialogue: 0,0:42:05.62,0:42:07.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Our S-Oke's Hatsu Butai!\N(=first performance)
Dialogue: 0,0:42:07.64,0:42:08.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's enjoy it!
Dialogue: 0,0:42:14.86,0:42:16.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Although it was just a very short time...
Dialogue: 0,0:42:18.39,0:42:20.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,it helped to make a big change in me
Dialogue: 0,0:42:21.58,0:42:23.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,it was really a Special Orchestra
Dialogue: 0,0:42:25.29,0:42:26.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,today it disbanded...
Dialogue: 0,0:42:29.97,0:42:30.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and then...
Dialogue: 0,0:42:32.53,0:42:34.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,everybody to his next stage...
Dialogue: 0,0:42:47.09,0:42:48.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So this is Momogaoka Music Academy....
Dialogue: 0,0:42:49.83,0:42:51.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Good, it seems that the level of the girls is also high!
Dialogue: 0,0:42:51.78,0:42:55.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just don't mess up the Oke by flopping, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:42:57.87,0:42:58.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shall we go now?
Dialogue: 0,0:43:07.84,0:43:11.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Alright, to say it again, I'm Miki Kiyora, playing violin.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:12.34,0:43:14.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kuroki Yasunori-kun, playing oboe.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:14.54,0:43:15.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kikuchi Tooru-kun, playing cello
Dialogue: 0,0:43:16.06,0:43:16.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yoroshiku ne!
Dialogue: 0,0:43:17.00,0:43:18.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kimura Tomohito-kun, playing violin
Dialogue: 0,0:43:18.93,0:43:19.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hi!
Dialogue: 0,0:43:19.68,0:43:21.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And, the last, as you already knew...
Dialogue: 0,0:43:21.18,0:43:23.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,is our Conductor, Chiaki Shinichi-kun
Dialogue: 0,0:43:23.24,0:43:23.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yoroshiku!
Dialogue: 0,0:43:24.10,0:43:26.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Aaah, I saw that Dream Color Classic,\Nwith the Special pin-up
Dialogue: 0,0:43:27.07,0:43:29.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I saw it too. Later please give us your autograph!
Dialogue: 0,0:43:29.26,0:43:32.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,First, let's discuss about the member formation\Namong ourselves, five members.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:33.09,0:43:36.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,For now, this is a simple Member List of the\Npeople I contacted...here...
Dialogue: 0,0:43:37.19,0:43:37.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Excuse me...
Dialogue: 0,0:43:38.32,0:43:40.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I have a timpani player I want to recommend...
Dialogue: 0,0:43:43.72,0:43:45.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Timpani: Okuyama Masumi
Dialogue: 0,0:43:50.52,0:43:54.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What is it? Eye contact between the Concert Master\Nand the Conductor right away?
Dialogue: 0,0:43:54.41,0:43:55.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:43:55.31,0:43:57.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ahhh...it looks like it will be enjoyable...
Dialogue: 0,0:43:57.97,0:43:58.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Right?
Dialogue: 0,0:43:59.52,0:44:00.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:00.43,0:44:01.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Right?
Dialogue: 0,0:44:05.64,0:44:08.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Lesson Instructor Change"\NPiano Division: 3rd Year Noda Megumi\NInstructor: Tanioka Hajime --> Eto Kozo
Dialogue: 0,0:44:08.20,0:44:09.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Eto Kozo....
Dialogue: 0,0:44:09.68,0:44:11.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's Harisen, isn't he?
Dialogue: 0,0:44:11.79,0:44:12.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes..
Dialogue: 0,0:44:13.82,0:44:15.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Elite Specialist
Dialogue: 0,0:44:15.57,0:44:16.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Eto Juku!!
Dialogue: 0,0:44:25.14,0:44:27.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Umm...you entered the wrong room!
Dialogue: 0,0:44:31.07,0:44:32.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's not the wrong room
Dialogue: 0,0:44:34.71,0:44:38.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm your Instructor from today
Dialogue: 0,0:44:38.31,0:44:39.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Eto Kozo!
Dialogue: 0,0:44:40.86,0:44:41.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yoroshiku!
Dialogue: 0,0:44:45.97,0:44:53.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is just a BETA version\NAny mistake will be corrected in the Final Release
Dialogue: 0,0:44:53.87,0:44:59.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you for watching!!\N*<<(o_o)>>* bye bye!!